<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{pageTitle}} - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex bg-slate-50">
  {{> common/sidebar-admin}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="flex-1 p-8">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a
              href="/admin/patient/list"
              class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 hover:bg-white rounded-xl border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all"
            >
              <i data-feather="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            </a>

            <div>
              <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">{{pageTitle}}</h1>
              <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">환자 기본 정보와 전체 예약 이력을 확인합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <section class="lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6 border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/60">
                <h2 class="font-bold text-slate-800">기본 정보</h2>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">환자 식별 정보와 등록된 연락처를 확인합니다.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="p-6 space-y-5">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">환자 ID</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">{{model.patientId}}</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">이름</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">{{model.name}}</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">연락처</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">{{model.phone}}</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">이메일</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">{{model.email}}</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">주소</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">{{model.address}}</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">메모</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">{{model.note}}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6 border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/60">
                <div>
                  <h2 class="font-bold text-slate-800">예약 이력</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">해당 환자의 전체 예약 및 접수 이력을 시간순으로 확인합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                  <thead>
                    <tr class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
                      <th class="p-4 font-medium">예약번호</th>
                      <th class="p-4 font-medium">날짜</th>
                      <th class="p-4 font-medium">시간</th>
                      <th class="p-4 font-medium">진료과</th>
                      <th class="p-4 font-medium">의사</th>
                      <th class="p-4 font-medium">상태</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
                    {{#model.reservationHistories}}
                      <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">{{reservationNumber}}</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-700">{{reservationDate}}</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-700">{{timeSlot}}</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-700">{{departmentName}}</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-700">{{doctorName}}</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">{{statusText}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/model.reservationHistories}}
                    {{^model.reservationHistories}}
                      <tr>
                        <td colspan="6" class="p-8 text-center text-slate-500">등록된 예약 이력이 없습니다.</td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/model.reservationHistories}}
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>
    feather.replace();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
